17:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Who Should Choose Which?"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"The ideal user for each platform differs considerably. Blackbox AI is best suited for developers wanting free code generation, quick code snippets, making it a strong choice if you fall into any of these categories. Sweep AI, meanwhile, shines for teams with large issue backlogs, automating simple code changes, which means it may be the better pick if your needs align with those use cases.\n\nFounded in 2022, Blackbox AI describes itself as \"AI-powered code autocomplete and search.\" Sweep AI, established in 2023, positions itself as \"AI junior developer that handles GitHub issues.\" Both platforms have been in the market for a similar duration, giving each ample time to refine their offerings and build a loyal user base."}]]}]
18:["$","div",null,{"className":"verdict-box","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Our Verdict"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"After analyzing all the data, **Sweep AI** comes out slightly ahead in this comparison, thanks to higher user ratings (6.0 vs 5.0), availability of a free plan. However, this does not mean Blackbox AI is a poor choice — far from it. Blackbox AI excels in its own right, particularly for developers wanting free code generation and quick code snippets.\n\nOur recommendation: if you value automates github issue resolution, go with Sweep AI. If free to use matters more to you, Blackbox AI is the way to go. Either way, both are solid platforms that have earned their place in the market."}]]}]
